brow text-amber-300\">Since 2010</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl font-playfair text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-snow text-balance md:text-6xl\">Born in the Himalayas, Built for Adventure</h1><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-xl font-lato text-lg text-snow/80\">A locally owned agency run by the guides who grew up beneath these peaks.</p></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-warm section-pad\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden \"><svg class=\"absolute inset-0 h-full w-full\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid slice\" viewBox=\"0 0 600 600\"><g fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#4D0014\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" style=\"opacity:0.07\"><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"60\" ry=\"42\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:0s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"108\" ry=\"78\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:0.6s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"156\" ry=\"114\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:1.2s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"204\" ry=\"150\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:1.7999999999999998s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"252\" ry=\"186\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:2.4s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"300\" ry=\"222\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:3s\"></ellipse><ellipse cx=\"300\" cy=\"300\" rx=\"348\" ry=\"258\" class=\"animate-pulse-ring\" style=\"transform-origin:300px 300px;animation-delay:3.5999999999999996s\"></ellipse></g></svg></div><div class=\"container-trek relative z-10 grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"relative h-[420px] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><img alt=\"Our guides on a Himalayan trail\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width:1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1528360983277-13d401cdc186%3Fw%3D1000%26q%3D80%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div><p class=\"eyebrow text-amber-600\">Our Story</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-playfair text-4xl font-bold text-green-900\">A team of locals with a shared love of the mountains</h2><p class=\"mt-5 font-lato leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Nepal Trek Agency began in 2010 in the narrow lanes of Boudha, Kathmandu, founded by a handful of guides who had spent their lives on these trails. We were tired of seeing visitors handed cookie-cutter itineraries by faceless operators — so we built something different.</p><p class=\"mt-4 font-lato leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Every trek we run is led by a guide born and raised in the Himalayas. We keep groups small, we look after our porters, and we treat the mountains with the respect they deserve. Fifteen years and a thousand expeditions later, that hasn&#x27;t changed.</p><a class=\"btn btn-amber group mt-8\" href=\"/contact\">Plan With Us <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-green-900 section-pad text-snow\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden \"><svg class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 h-full w-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 1200 400\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMax slice\" fill=\"none\"><g class=\"animate-parallax-x\" style=\"opacity:0.06\"><path d=\"M-50 400 L200 140 L380 400Z\" fill=\"#f8f6f0\"></path><path d=\"M250 400 L520 90 L760 400Z\" fill=\"#f8f6f0\"></path><path d=\"M650 400 L900 160 L1250 400Z\" fill=\"#f8f6f0\"></path></g><g style=\"opacity:0.09\"><path d=\"M-50 400 L150 220 L420 400Z\" fill=\"#f8f6f0\"></path><path d=\"M350 400 L640 180 L980 400Z\" fill=\"#f8f6f0\"></path><path d=\"M520 165 L560 200 L600 175\" stroke=\"#003893\" stroke-width=\"3\" opacity=\"0.5\"></path></g></svg></div><div class=\"container-trek relative z-10\"><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-4 text-amber-600\">Our Journey</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h2 class=\"font-playfair text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-balance md:text-5xl text-snow\">Milestones on the Trail</h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\">2010</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-snow/80\">Founded in Boudha, Kathmandu by a small team of Sherpa and Gurung guides.</p></div><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\">2013</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-snow/80\">Became a registered TAAN member and licensed by the Nepal Tourism Board.</p></div><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\">2016</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-snow/80\">Expanded into restricted regions — Upper Mustang, Manaslu and Tsum Valley.</p></div><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\">2020</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-snow/80\">Launched our Leave No Trace programme and porter welfare charter.</p></div><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\">2024</p><p class=\"mt-3 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-snow/80\">Crossed 1,000 successful expeditions with a 98% satisfaction rate.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-warm section-pad\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden \"><svg class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full\" viewBox=\"0 0 1200 120\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\"><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:0px 120px;animation-delay:0s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"0,60 -16,120 16,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"0,78 -22,114 22,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:88px 120px;animation-delay:0.3s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"88,38 72,120 104,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"88,56 66,114 110,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:140px 120px;animation-delay:0.6s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"140,16 124,120 156,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"140,34 118,114 162,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:228px 120px;animation-delay:0.8999999999999999s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"228,60 212,120 244,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"228,78 206,114 250,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:280px 120px;animation-delay:1.2s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"280,38 264,120 296,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"280,56 258,114 302,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:368px 120px;animation-delay:0s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"368,16 352,120 384,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"368,34 346,114 390,114\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon></g><g class=\"animate-sway\" style=\"transform-origin:420px 120px;animation-delay:0.3s;opacity:0.08\"><polygon points=\"420,60 404,120 436,120\" fill=\"#4D0014\"></polygon><polygon points=\"4