 the narrow lanes of Boudha, Kathmandu, founded by a handful of guides who had spent their lives on these trails. We were tired of seeing visitors handed cookie-cutter itineraries by faceless operators — so we built something different.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 font-lato leading-relaxed text-stone-800\",\"children\":\"Every trek we run is led by a guide born and raised in the Himalayas. We keep groups small, we look after our porters, and we treat the mountains with the respect they deserve. Fifteen years and a thousand expeditions later, that hasn't changed.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"btn btn-amber group mt-8\",\"children\":[\"Plan With Us \",[\"$\",\"svg\",null,{\"viewBox\":\"0 0 24 24\",\"fill\":\"none\",\"stroke\":\"currentColor\",\"strokeWidth\":1.8,\"strokeLinecap\":\"round\",\"strokeLinejoin\":\"round\",\"width\":18,\"height\":18,\"className\":\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"path\",null,{\"d\":\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"}]}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"relative overflow-hidden bg-green-900 section-pad text-snow\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L8\",null,{\"variant\":\"mountains\",\"tone\":\"light\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-trek relative z-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"eyebrow\":\"Our Journey\",\"title\":\"Milestones on the Trail\",\"tone\":\"light\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L1f\",\"2010\",{\"i\":0,\"className\":\"relative rounded-2xl border border-snow/10 bg-green-800/50 p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-playfair text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400\",\"children\":\"2010\"}],\"$L21\"]}],\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\"]}]]}]]}],\"$L26\",\"$L27\"],[\"$L28\"],\"$L29\"]}]\n2a:[]\n17:\"$W2a\"\n18:[\"$\",\"$2\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{\"children\":\"$L2c\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"c